  "title": "Associate Educator (English)",
  "description": "<p>MathSci Synergy is currently looking for interested candidates to take up the role of associate educator with us.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Min diploma graduate.</p>\n<p>2. Strong interest in teaching English for Primary/Secondary</p>\n<p>3. Enjoys teaching through interaction rather than worksheet based classes.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Think you got what it takes for the job?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Email us or whatsapp your resume to</p>\n<p>pathfindertuition@gmail.com OR +65 8113 2816.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Kindly state the subject your are interested to teach, outlet location, availability and where looking for long or short term commitment.</p>",
